ext.ojalgo.pride

Class DataSnapshot

  • java.lang.Object
    • ext.ojalgo.pride.DataSnapshot
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class DataSnapshot
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A DataSnapshot encapsulates an EntityBean. There is (should be) only one snapshot per row in the database. They cannot be modified and are automatically kept in sync with database changes. If you call getEntityBean() you will get a copy of the current database values.
    Author:
    apete
